item.title: Know no fear Warhammer 40K journal
item.description: And they shall know no fear! When you stand in defiance of the enemies of Mankind, in Warhammer 40K there is one thing a marine must not know! Make your everyday journaling more personal, private, and stylish with this matte hardcover journal. Available in 5.75"x8", with 150 lined pages, these sturdy hardcover journals are fully customizable on the front and on the back covers. The matte laminate coating on the cover will make them stay true to your personal style.
